{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those are the other things that we missed, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never had any artistic kind of education or [INAUDIBLE] maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we never learned about music, so I'm useless at music.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never had any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For-- for-- for about 10 years, I suppose, we never really heard music, because later on, we were not allowed to have radios, you see?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everything was only what we could do ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we'd given up our pianos, and so we didn't do any of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was another thing that I'd really forgotten about, until quite recently, was that we had these pianos and that my father played them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we moved to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Amsterdam, there is a Jewish area, not far from the central station, really, where most of the Dutch Jews lived for centuries, really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we went to live in the southern part of Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's called the Rivers Area, [DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Rivers Area, where all the straits were named after Dutch rivers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to live in Vechtstraat-- Vecht was a river somewhere in Holland-- in one of these apartment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have these long apartment blocks in the streets with three stories above each other, a bit like townhouses, but all kind of joined together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a typical Dutch invention, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the films that you see of Anne Frank and all that sort of thing, you keep seeing these streets with those sort of houses.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived in one of those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, actually, Anne Frank lived just around the corner in Merwedeplein.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another good word to say in English, Merwedeplein.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And lots of the German refugees-- because the Franks came from Frankfurt in 1933, so they came a lot earlier than us.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
